{"tid":933760,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己身分比人盜用 洗唔洗報咗警先","createTime":"2018-12-08T17:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T17:52:06.000Z","uid":109631,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a69216491dd96ef1aeb4d10a6ddd2ae9e446c38d","tid":933760,"uid":109631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"話說今日突然學校email account 收到個奇怪email<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhgQdRv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhgQdRv.png&h=6093247c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個google drive有我身分證copy<br />\n<br />\n跟住夜少少就電話係咁彈notification 出來<br />\n想掃走佢點知突然打咗電話過去<br />\n咁佢即係知道埋我電話號碼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我諗佢要拎嘅都拎晒，可以做好多嘢例如用我個名借錢嗰啲，洗唔洗報定警先<br />\n<br />\n利申 早排工作關係被迫開WeChat同支那寶,而家每一日都生活得好不安好過敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a578ef47d52bfa9223f20e2752bc9dc5ec1a3016","tid":933760,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:37:06.000Z","msg":"有咩工要開wechat同支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463b2dec9ad9b8800d52c301027bcfc7b97f0a43","tid":933760,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"終わりだ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7ae46dde5e00e9aed700479dce46759dbf6ab9","tid":933760,"uid":109631,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a578ef47d52bfa9223f20e2752bc9dc5ec1a3016","tid":933760,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:37:06.000Z","msg":"有咩工要開wechat同支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:39:51.000Z","msg":"當你身邊大陸人仲多過local...唔關工嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31d143686eec45e8b9d1fd139acb6bd556fb612","tid":933760,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"